race.comment: IGOTMYMINDONYOU (3) has been thereabouts and is another overdue. Placed oly try this course and distance. Drawn out last couple but from the low gate should enjoy a soft run here and gets his chance. GALAGACISCO (1) was a close-up fifth fresh then narrowly missed again last time at Nhill. This is no easier and has drawn wide but is another close to breaking through. MISS LIL (10) ran on well for third two back then just missed the frame latest. That run was off her best and she can improve here. SUN AND WAVES (11) resumed from a long break with a solid run and will strip much fitter. Aided by the claim and although yet to place has run a couple of fair races.
